    "name": "Freezing WHAT IF...",
    "steam_appid": 3126650,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Another World of Freezing that never existed in history: 'Freezing WHAT IF...'</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A fan fiction game that brings to life an alternate history of the Freezing universe, reimagined as a multiverse!</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Based on the globally popular battle heroine manga Freezing, this game offers a fresh and unique experience.</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>This game is a fan fiction project officially produced with permission from the original author. It features a different storyline from the original work.</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, humanity was invaded by &quot;Nova,&quot; beings from another dimension, plunging the world into an unprecedented crisis.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using their unique ability called &quot;Freezing,&quot; Nova immobilized time and space, rendering humanity's weapons useless while threatening mass extinction with their devastating self-destruct mechanism.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In response, humanity created [Pandoras], chosen girls with extraordinary powers far beyond human limits,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and [Limiters], chosen boys who can neutralize Nova's Freezing ability and amplify the Pandoras' powers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Together, they became humanity's last line of resistance against Nova.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, despite their efforts, humanity suffered a catastrophic defeat at the hands of Nova, seemingly beyond recovery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many Limiters perished, while the Pandoras, humanity's last hope, succumbed to mental corruption from Nova, leading to amnesia or berserk behavior, accelerating humanity's march toward extinction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Amidst this chaos, you are entrusted with leading the remaining human forces against Nova.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a Limiter with the rare ability to empathize with multiple Pandoras at once,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >you offer humanity a renewed hope to stand against Nova once more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must manage and develop the remaining human territories, building strength and forces to counter Nova.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must also locate scattered Pandoras, revive them with all your might, and unite to fight the threat of Nova.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through a combination of strategy simulation and turn-based battle RPG systems,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >experience a brand-new &quot;What If...?&quot; take on the world of Freezing, different from the original!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[The Threat to Humanity, Nova]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126650/extras/c9edf749518d88b671f278e91d1cc86a.avif?t=1741756282\" width=600 height=288 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[The Hope of Humanity, Pandora]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126650/extras/8619f95c21cc55b5cb09993ece352e6c.avif?t=1741756282\" width=600 height=276 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >And... your story, carrying the fate of the world, begins here!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《 Stand Against Nova as the Commander of the Resistance! 》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126650/extras/9654426f4df2aa937011a43d3c269722.avif?t=1741756282\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126650/extras_big/9654426f4df2aa937011a43d3c269722.avif?t=1741756282 width=800 height=464 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secure and develop bases to grow your power. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Resist Nova's relentless invasions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《 Awaken Pandoras as a Limiter and Lead Them in Battle! 》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126650/extras/359fd3db662f0c7a4003f882c9dac689.poster.avif?t=1741756282\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126650/extras/359fd3db662f0c7a4003f882c9dac689.webm?t=1741756282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126650/extras/359fd3db662f0c7a4003f882c9dac689.mp4?t=1741756282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your unique ability of mental empathy to strengthen Pandoras and wield the special technique, Freezing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Support and command Pandoras with your Limiter powers to lead them to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy diverse battle scenes, featuring each Pandora's unique skills and costume destruction effects. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《 Rescue and Awaken Missing Pandoras to Join Your Ranks!! 》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126650/extras/5b4a604f82e91d2c7e57b3b57d4454ac.avif?t=1741756282\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126650/extras_big/5b4a604f82e91d2c7e57b3b57d4454ac.avif?t=1741756282 width=800 height=466 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find Pandoras who went missing during the last Nova invasion and save them from mental corruption.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They will once again stand with you as humanity's protectors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
